Preheat grill to medium heat. Cook and stir onion, green pepper and red pepper in hot oil in skillet on medium heat until crisp-tender. Stir in steak sauce and horseradish. Remove from heat; cover to keep warm. Shape meat into 4 patties. Grill patties 5 minutes on each side or until cooked through. Top bottom half of each roll with patty; cover with 1/4 of the vegetable mixture and top half of roll.